Thomas Partey has rejected Atletico Madrid's contract proposal, which has been described by Rahman Usman, a Ghanaian journalist who has communication channels and knowledge of Thomas Partey and his family as 'garbage'. [@TheAFCBeII]<br />
<br />
Ghanaian journalist Rahman Usman on Partey's reaction to the speculation : &quot;He will definitely be flattered of the news of his association with Arsenal and that he will inevitably be eager to hear from them.&quot;

